title: Marvel Now - Week 10/09/2013
description:
Hello everybody! Another week, another Marvel NOW! Comics Pack!
The most noteworthy comics of this week are:

- Infinity 4, new chapter of this great event (Personally, I think is the best "great event" since Civil War)
- Fearless Defenders 10 and Superior Spider-Man Team Up 4, both Infinity Tie-Ins
- X-Men 6, new chapter of the Mutant Maxi-Event "Battle for the Atom"

That's all for this week. See ya next time!
Bye!
